quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  40,41,"Ko onon yo yim…ìe am, ko wa…ói si mi…óo nodda on e da…óirgol hayrude aduna e laakara, gom…óinde Allah, golla ko mo∆¥∆¥i, onon, hi…óon noddira lam naatugol Yiite, …óa…ì…ìirgol lam, yeddugol Allah?"
  40,42,"Hi…óon noddira lam e meere mon nden, jortagol no mi yeddira Allah, mi kafida Mo e go…ó…óum goo, ko mi alanaa …óum ganndal, hara non, min mi…óo noddude on e gom…óingol Allah, Foolu…óo Mo gooto foolataa, Surroowo bakkaatu, Mawnu…óo haforangol jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen."
  40,43,"Tigi on, ko noddoton lam e mun kon, gom…óingol …óoftoo, noddaandu goonga woo alanaa …óum aduna, wanaa laakara, gooto kadi noototaakau ndun noddaandu. E wonnde pellet, ruttorde men nden, en fow, ko ka Allah tun, e wonnde fantim…ìe geddi …ìen, ko …ìen woni yim…ìe Yiite …ìen, duumotoo…ìe ton, √ëalnde Darngal."
  40,44,"∆Åe salii laa…ìal makko reedu ngal, o wi'ani …ìe: aray nde anndoton, fii ko mi laa…ìani on reedu kon, nimson salaare mon nden; min non, mi fawii fiyaaku am on fow, e Allah Gooto On. Pellet, huunde suu…óaaki Allah, e golle jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen."
  40,45,"Allah da…óndi mo, boneeji …ói …ìe fewjunannoo mo …óin, fii warugol mo, O huu…ìitiri yim…ìe Fir'awna …ìen, lepte yoolagol. Allah yooli mo kanko Fir'awna, e konu ma…ì…ìe ngun fow."
  40,46,"Caggal …ìe maayii, …ìe wee…ìitoyte e Yiite ngen, ka genaale ma…ì…ìe, bimmbi e kiikii…óe. √ëalnde Darngal darotoo (wi'oyte): Naadee jokkunoo…ìe Fir'awna …ìen, ka …ìuri sa…ótude e lepte. Sabu ko …ìe yeddiraynoo kon, …ìe fenna …ìe falatoo e laawol Allah ngol."
  40,47,"Janto an Nulaa…óo, tuma jokkunoo…ìe …ìen yeddondiroyta e jokkanoo…ìe …ìen, ka nder Yiite, …ìe wi'ana …ìen jokkonoo…ìe towninitinoo…ìe: Menen, ko onon men jokkunoo aduna, e majjere, taw si on duncanay men ge…ìal e lepte Allah …óen, ronnditano…óon men …óe?"
  40,48,"Townitinii…ìe jokkanoo…ìe …ìen kadi wi'a: En fow mee…óen, jokkunoo…ìe e jokkanoo…ìe fow, hino e Yiite ngen, gooto ronnditantaako go…ó…óo goo, ge…ìal e lepte laakara …óen. Tawde pellet, Alah √±aawii hakkunde jeyaa…ìe …ìen. O yo…ìiti kala e ko hanndi e mun kon."
  40,49,"Wonaa…ìe lepteede …ìen ka Yiite fow wi'ana Malaa'ika'en, ayninaa…ìe Yiite ngen, tuma …ìe ta∆¥ii yaltugol e magge, ruttoo aduna, fii tuubugol: Toranee men Joomi mon, O hoynana men √±alaande wootere, e …óee lepte duumii…óe."